{"tid":527320,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[Netflix Marvel] 香港需要 Punisher 定 Daredevil","createTime":"2018-01-12T13:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T21:36:56.000Z","uid":8495,"like":136,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1a01820707b4cc1a34760742b9e6c59f769590f9","tid":527320,"uid":8495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T13:54:50.000Z","msg":"大家都係以暴易暴，覺得警犬無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 但有唔同底線<br />\n<br />\nPunisher 唔相信法律可以制裁罪犯，用自己既方法殺晒d 壞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDaredevil 相信法律，以唔殺人既方法捉壞人，交比法律制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個人認為邊個方法有效係要睇社會既情況<br />\n係Hell's Kitchen 咁腐敗既地方，punisher 有效d<br />\n係developed 左既社區，dd 有效d<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家香港，算係一個比較developed 既城市，但班警犬就無撚用既，有錢人為左奶大陸鞋咩都做得出<br />\n咁你地覺得香港係需要 Punisher 定 Daredevil 呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Punisher <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Daredevil"},{"pid":"87d9602c2bfc8fc596d15ec57a0c7483e0d25e37","tid":527320,"uid":100236,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T13:56:54.000Z","msg":"係連登問一定係罰叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d88765d480ac83a42fd9c1228e260c2ee5c9fc","tid":527320,"uid":60500,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:01:11.000Z","msg":"而家香港連警察都信唔過，你覺得邊個比較適合香港？"},{"pid":"eac97c09fa717edeaa9360190fc1860bf29db828","tid":527320,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:01:38.000Z","msg":"兩套都好撚好睇"},{"pid":"2b1fd376c3a5492e82f11c3ee4517b0fa512dc55","tid":527320,"uid":49151,"like":1,"disl